<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA60">
<l>peṟṟam piṇaimarutam pēymulai māccakaṭa</l>
<l>muṟṟakkāt tūṭupō yuṇṭutaittuk – kaṟṟuk</l>
<l>kuṇilai viḷaṅkaṉikkuk koṇṭeṟintāṉ veṟṟip</l>
<l>paṇilamvāy vaittukantāṉ paṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who , successfully protecting the cows, going in between the entwined myrobalam trees,</l>
<l>drinking from the breast of the demoness, kicking the horse cart,</l>
<l>took a calf stick [and] threw it for the woodapple fruits is the one who once</l>
<l>rejoiced in putting the conch to [his] mouth in victory.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
